1. Import this project in eclipse.
2. change the database details in props folder under WebContent folder.
 i.e change username, password and connection url.
i have used MYSQL database.
3. There is a sql script which need to be executed before running the application.
4. Deploy this web application on apachetomcat7 server.
6. Please use JAVA 7.
8. After deploying the application on server you can access it using below url
  http://localhost:portnumber/PrizyPricer
9. This application is built on spring framework, all the rquired jars are present in the application.

Note: portnumber is the port on which tomcat server is started.
